msgctxt "Community engagement section - inviting users to provide feedback and report issues"
msgid "<strong>Your voice matters!</strong> Whether you've got a brilliant idea, spotted a bug, or just want to share your experience - we're listening. Head over to our <strong>GitHub repository</strong> to open an issue or start a discussion. Every piece of feedback helps us build better tools for you."
